data.description: Check out this great 1-story home located in the established neighborhood of Pepperidge near Madison High School. This 3b/2b 2cg is 1727 sq ft offers a new Water Heater-June 2023.  Custom wood shutters, no carpet, roof is only 5 yrs old, Trane 14-seer AC installed 2018. High ceilings, large backyard with mature trees and a large patio. Only minutes from the Forum, IKEA, and Rolling Oaks Mall. Come see this home and make it yours today!
